name: minnesota-school-district-boundaries-sy2008-2009
notes: This file represents the boundaries of all public school districts in the state of Minnesota for school year 2008-2009. Minnesota school districts report any changes to their elementary, middle and high school attendance area boundaries on a yearly basis. This file is maintained at the Department of Education, but is also supplied to the State of Minnesota Legislative Coordinating Commission GIS Office and the Land Management Information Center (LMIC). This school district file was dissolved from a file containing both the school district and attendance boundaries to produce just school district boundaries.
